    "subType": "mutation",
    "description": "<p>You may exude venom as an On Turn action at the cost of one System Strain. If imbibed or applied by a bladed weapon attack or body weaponry, it does 1d8 damage plus the user&rsquo;s level to subjects susceptible to poison for the rest of the scene. The user may make the toxin non-lethal simply by lessening the dosage. Envenoming a weapon with this toxin takes a Main Action and the toxin spoils after a scene, though it can last through multiple hits. A given victim can be harmed by this poison only once per scene.</p>",
